### Create petty cash
POST {{baseUrl}}/petty-cash
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Office Petty Cash",
  "totalAmount": 3000,
  "notes": "Initial petty cash for supplies"
}


### Update petty cash
PUT {{baseUrl}}/petty-cash/{{pettyCashId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Office Petty Cash Updated",
  "totalAmount": 4000,
  "notes": "Added more funds"
}


### Get petty cash by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/petty-cash/{{pettyCashId}}


### Get all petty cash
GET {{baseUrl}}/petty-cash


### Delete petty cash
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/petty-cash/{{pettyCashId}}
